<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <title>TÜV SÜD GRC Connect Knowledge Base</title>
	<link type="text/css" href="css/dashboardhelp.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>

    <h2>TÜV SÜD GRC Connect Knowledge Base - Inspections Dashboard</h2>


    <div id="content" class="setPrimary">

        <div>
            <a href="DashboardHelp.aspx">Back to the general Knowledge Base for Dashboards</a>
        </div>
  
        <div id="contentInner">

            <div id="dashboardInspection" class="content">
                <h2>Inspections Dashboard</h2>
                <p class="contentP">
                    The Inspections Dashboard contains information about the inspections (surveys) that TÜV SÜD GRC has provided to you historically in addition to those that are scheduled for the future.  
                </p>
                <p>
                    <img src="images/Insp.jpg" style="float:left;border:1px solid #CFD8DC" />
                </p>
                    <h4>Definitions</h4>
                    <ul style="float:left;width:40%;">
                    <li>
                        Initial Inspection: An inspection for a location that had never been previously inspected.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Pending Not Scheduled Inspection: A future inspection for which a date of inspection has not yet been determined.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Pending Scheduled Inspection: A future inspection for which a date of inspection has been determined.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Pending Inspection: An inspection that is either a Pending Not Scheduled Inspection or a Pending Scheduled Inspection.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Completed Inspection: An inspection where the collection of information has been completed.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Pending Report: A report that has not yet been submitted to the client though the inspection has been completed.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Completed Report: A report that has been submitted to the client after the inspection has been completed.
                    </li>
                    </ul>
            </div>

            <div id="ReportStatus" class="content">
                <h3>Report Status</h3>
                <p class="contentP">
                    The Report Status chart shows the number of completed and pending reports for the selected service and contract year. 
                </p>
                    <img src="images/InspReportStatus.jpg"  style="float:left;border:1px solid #CFD8DC" />
            </div>

            <div id="InspStatus" class="content">
                <h3>Inspection Status</h3>
                <p class="contentP">
                    The Inspection Status chart and associated table show the number of completed and pending inspections for the selected service and contract year.  The pending inspections
                    are separated into Pending Scheduled and Pending Not Scheduled inspections.
                </p>
                    <img src="images/InspStatus.jpg"  style="float:left;border:1px solid #CFD8DC" />
            </div>

            <div id="InspByYear" class="content">
                <h3>Inspections By Year</h3>
                <p class="contentP">
                    The Inspections By Year chart shows the number of historical completed inspections by year.  Initial inspections are separated from those that are not initial inspections.
                </p>
                    <img src="images/InspByYear.jpg"  style="float:left;border:1px solid #CFD8DC" />
                    <ul style="float:left;width:40%;">
                    <li>
                        Closed Recommendations = Recommendations with Conf. Completed, Rptd. Completed and Removed statuses, grouped by the Status Date Year of the closure.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Risk Improvement - See definition of "Risk Improvement", above.
                    </li>
                    </ul>
            </div>

            <div id="PendingInsp" class="content">
                <h3>Pending Inspections</h3>
                <p class="contentP">
                    The map and table on the Pending Inspections tab show the inspections that are pending for the current and next two calendar months.
                </p>
                    <img src="images/InspPending.jpg"  style="float:left;border:1px solid #CFD8DC" />
            </div>


        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
